reviewText: It was a hilariously terrible movie! I only took off a star because of two fight scenes -- which were a bit on the self-conscious side, to the point that they were obnoxious rather than funny. OTHER THAN THAT, a delight!
Stupid but funny. Low budget scfi comedy.
Nice sequel to "The Sheriff And The Satellite Kid". If you like Bud Spencer you'll more than likely like this movie with a touch of sci-fi. These type films entertain you, but won't win any Oscars.
